{"tid":2087024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七一上街是拿腳頭砸自己的石","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:10:01.000Z","uid":169112,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d345edb6b75f97f48c8512f09452221dfe11dc2","tid":2087024,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"【愛惜你的石和腳】<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法正式出台，連無神論的阿確都不小心感動得說了句「感謝主」，連忙細聲補充一句「主是黨」後不禁感嘆：「真的好，香港社會動盪的時期有機會了結了！」<br />\n<br />\n而好消息更是浪接浪，亡我之心不死的美帝總算中了公子獻頭，正式拿石頭砸自己的腳，取消香港的特殊待遇。這樣一來，中國難免成為最大羸家。因為上海總算可以超越香港，成為新的金融中心；而且金融中心就是金融中心，不用搞甚麼「國際」金融中心，從此「只有一國，沒有國際」，中國就是新時代的王者。<br />\n<br />\n黨中央送的這份大禮，正好用明天一整個公眾假期來慶祝；然而慶祝歸慶祝，為預防疾病我們還是應該留在室內，畢竟去年的升旗都已經移師室內。否則，我們上街慶祝就是拿腳頭砸自己的石。<br />\n<br />\n砸自己的石好還是砸自己的腳好？敢情是自己的腳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDiUmFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDiUmFw.jpg&h=32c13103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/3075196769237135/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCorrectness%2Fphotos%2Fa.1282790118477818%2F3075196769237135%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e1a796ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/3075196769237135/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"b19da54d0a1e1ae46353ae1062ead1306c78cbe3","tid":2087024,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f9274484a1d33dd9072f71c48ff62f0b9cb7efdf","tid":2087024,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d760915f701938df565583a5047a4cbc7166dafc","tid":2087024,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"799e8e2ea68b2d5624f351f40253e8af37ce4772","tid":2087024,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"}]}